Foot-and-mouth disease, Mongolia
--------------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 25 Apr 2014 from Dr Bolortuya Purevsuren, Deputy Director and Chief Veterinary Officer, Veterinary and Animal Breeding Agency, Ministry for Industry and Agriculture, Ulaanbaatar, Mongolia

Summary
Report type: follow-up report no 3 (final report)
Date of start of the event: 26 Jan 2014
Date of pre-confirmation of the event: 30 Jan 2014
Report date: 25 Apr 2014
Date submitted to OIE: 25 Apr 2014
Date event resolved: 4 Apr 2014
Reason for notification: reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 28 Oct 2013
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: Foot and mouth disease virus
Serotype: O
Nature of diagnosis: clinical, laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country
Related reports: immediate notification (31 Jan 2014)
Follow-up report no 1 (4 Feb 2014)
Follow-up report no 2 (24 Feb 2014)
Follow-up report no 3 (25 Apr 2014)

New outbreaks (1)
Outbreak 1: Khuliin dersen us, Eldev bag, Dalanjargalan soum, Dornogovi
Date of start of the outbreak: 6 Mar 2014
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: farm
Affected animals
